# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# BSI (Blaze Sports Intel) — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your keys.
# Keys marked [FREE] work without any API key.
# Keys marked [TRIAL] have free trial tiers.
# Keys marked [ENTERPRISE] require sales contact.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Sportradar MLB v8 (ABS Challenge Data) ──────────────────────────────────
# [TRIAL] Free 30-day trial: https://developer.sportradar.com/member/register
# Process: Register → Add MLB Trial → Key appears in dashboard
# Rate limit: 1 QPS (trial), 10 QPS (production)
# Auth: Query parameter ?api_key=YOUR_KEY
# Base URL: https://api.sportradar.com/mlb/trial/v8/en
# Postman: https://www.postman.com/sportradar-media-apis/sportradar-media-apis/documentation/4rr5lu8/sportradar-mlb-v8
SPORTRADAR_API_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SPORTRADAR_KEY=

# ─── SkillCorner (Broadcast-Derived Tracking) ────────────────────────────────
# [ENTERPRISE] No public signup — contact support@skillcorner.com
# Auth: Username/password (not API key)
# Python SDK: pip install skillcorner
# [FREE] Open data (10 A-League matches): https://github.com/SkillCorner/opendata
# BSI uses the open data adapter when no key is set.
SKILLCORNER_API_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SKILLCORNER_KEY=

# ─── Biomechanics (KinaTrax / Rapsodo / PitcherNet / Driveline) ──────────────
# KinaTrax: [ENTERPRISE] No public API — stadium-installed systems only
# Rapsodo:  [ENTERPRISE] Hardware-coupled, no public developer API
# PitcherNet: [ENTERPRISE] IP owned by Baltimore Orioles, not open-sourced
# Driveline: [FREE] Open biomechanics dataset on GitHub (CC BY 4.0)
#            https://github.com/drivelineresearch/openbiomechanics
# BSI uses Driveline open data when no key is set.
BIOMECHANICS_API_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_BIOMECHANICS_KEY=

# ─── Baseball Savant / Statcast ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# [FREE] No API key required — public CSV endpoint
# Endpoint: https://baseballsavant.mlb.com/statcast_search/csv
# Limit: ~25,000 rows per query, use 5-7 day windows
# BSI fetches directly from Savant — no key needed.

# ─── Highlightly (College Sports) ────────────────────────────────────────────
HIGHLIGHTLY_API_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_HIGHLIGHTLY_KEY=

# ─── Anthropic (BSI Agent) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# ─── RapidAPI (Multi-sport scores) ───────────────────────────────────────────
RAPIDAPI_KEY=
